be a good place to hear such
music, and more performances
in Roberts to seat everyone cost
much more money.
Vocal jazz, with groups such
as members, Hendricks, and
japan seem to be able to transfers the airplane-danger effect better than other styles.
thriller, since only three concerts remain to be scheduled
after cooperation With the
other campus departments, it
seems unlike to give more
than one concert in the jazz
idiom if a balanced program is
[0 be maintained.
It is hoped that the proposed
social increase that is to be pre»
center to the trustees will end
able the various social committees to meet the rapidly l‘lying costs and to present the
campus with high quality
events.
